  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.maven.plugin.ContextEnabled, org.apache.maven.plugin.Mojo

    @Mojo(name="generate-sonar-rules",
      requiresProject=false)
 @Execute(goal="generate-sonar-rules",
         lifecycle="sonar",
         phase=TEST)
public class ConvertRulesToSonarMojo
extends CodeReviewNoForkMojo

    This goal generates a "rules.xml" file which can be put in "$SONAR_HOME/conf" directory of Sonarqube.

    This will enable the import of custom rules in Sonarqube.
